BatteryLevel NEWS
=================

CHANGES WITH 0.2a (The Documentation Update):

* Provided NEWS, ChangeLog and such documentation files.

* Added some examples files at directory examples.

* Systemd service provided don't use `--forced` by default.

* Configuration file has a new property: forced.

* Do not try to load module if no beep will sound.

* Option to make and install a package for Arch Linux with:

    make arch-package
    make arch-install
